data.description: Discover this charming townhouse, perfectly situated just a few minutes away from the downtown area. This delightful residence features two cozy bedrooms and two bathrooms. Additionally, it boasts a separate office complete with a fireplace, an inviting Arizona room, and a convenient one-car garage. The main living area is freshly updated with new laminate flooring, adding to the home's appeal. Experience the ideal Northern Arizona living with this property. Enjoy the benefit of low HOA fees, which cover water, sewer, and trash services
